main event: Multiple unidentified objects were observed drifting over Lake Okeechobee, Florida.
interesting points: The objects were observed drifting earthward over the lake.
Contact with the Maxwell Flight Service Center verified the existence of flares in the specified area of Florida at the same time of the sighting.
The R-47 type aircraft had conducted a training mission in the area at the time of the sighting.
The length of the observation is unknown.
The number of objects was many, but not counted.
